profile:
The Anything Guys was founded in 2005 by Tom Rheaume. It has since grown to a strong 10 person team. 
 
Our focus is to supply Ottawa residents with a professional, affordable service that is a one-stop shop for both commercial and residential clients, specializing in pretty much anything! We pride ourselves in our ability to offer a large variety of different household and property related services, big or small, irregular or mainstream, which can be found on our services page. 

This is what you receive with every job you book with us: 
 
Convenience: One number, one main contact and an experienced team to handle most any home and garden renovation and maintenance need. 

Quality Work: Qualified tradesmen who will do the work diligently and to the highest standards
Reliability & Consistency: Good communication is very important to us. If a customer changes the scope of work, we notify them of changes to timelines, schedules and budgets. 

Customer Service: Enjoy a positive experience working with TAG.  

Fair pricing that comes with full Insurance: Our pricing is competitive and we are fully insurued which means you aren't at risk when hiring us for your renovation or landscaping work.
name: The Anything Guys

profile:
Instant Lawns is one of Ottawa’s elite curb appeal experts specializing in re-sodding and new lawn installation. Our mission is to provide the most professional, convenient and efficient service the world of landscaping has ever seen. We are very proud to be one of Ottawa's lawn installation experts among the leaders of our industry. We have in place an ethos of extraordinary customer service. We swiftly answer you when you call or email us, are extremely reliable, always deliver what we promise you (on time AND on budget) and use only the best products and materials on every installation.

profile:
EverGreen Landscape Ottawa / Interlocking Brick Ottawa has been satisfying clients in the Ottawa and surrounding area since 1984. Beginning as a small company offering Ottawa landscaping services and snow blowing removal to residential customers, within the second year EverGreen Landscape Ottawa (EGL) client base grew to 150 and since then they have expanded. 

Servicing both residential and commercial clients over the years, EverGreen Landscape Ottawa, Interlock Ottawa offers many services such as commercial property maintenance - shopping centres, apartment buildings, various repair work including foundations, to design and construction of various types of interlock landscape in Ottawa such as interlock patios, interlocking driveways, retaining walls, interlocking steps, interlock pool stone landscape, gardening, decks, and fences - just to mention a few. Landscaping equipment rental, supply and delivery of landscaping soils are also available. 

Known for their creative talent in interlocking brick projects and having full certification by ICPI (Interlocking Concrete Pavement Institute) and as a Techo-Pro Certified Contractor - you will be pleased that you have chosen EverGreen Landscape Ottawa, Interlock Ottawa for your outdoor Ottawa landscaping project.

Services Include:
Interlocking Brick
Patios
Walkways
Driveways
Pool Interlock and water features
Decks and fences
Design and construction
Snow blowing

profile:
Making Your Yard A Part of Your Home!
http://www.gfxottawa.ca
We at Ground FX Landscape Construction are pleased to offer our valued Ottawa area clients unique landscape knowledge, skill and design ideas that add beauty, usefulness and enjoyment to their outdoor spaces.

We help clients with all size landscaping projects from a small re-leveling of an existing walkway to a complete property makeover including in-ground swimming pool, water features and interlocking pavers.

Swimming Pool fill-in and re-landscaping service also available.

We present to our clients, complimentary consultations and quotations, creative design options, site plans, professional knowledge, expertise and installation.

Our goal is to work successfully with our clients to achieve a product which we are proud to present and that our clients will benefit from for as long as they own their property.

Our company has full liability insurance, and is WSIB covered. Don’t take any chances!!
We look forward to speaking with you about your landscaping projects. http://www.gfxottawa.ca
